": "大啊。", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:09", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "那你去跟你老闆講啊，勞動部就講了，", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:10", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "不上班自己去跟老闆講。", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:10", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "被隔離和天災不請假 雇主也無給付義務", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:10", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_content": "比照SARS隔離期間強制公假才合理吧", "push_ipdatetime": "49.217.32.91 01/27 17:11", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "AnpingTW"}, {"push_content": "被隔離不上班不然要醫院幫你跟老闆說?", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:11", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_content": "病假還有半薪 天災假一毛都沒有", "push_ipdatetime": "115.82.14.165 01/27 17:11", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "Serisu"}, {"push_content": "你以為勞工無法上班損失的只有勞工？", "push_ipdatetime": "42.77.219.134 01/27 17:12", "push_tag": "噓", "push_userid": "rahim03"}, {"push_content": "工總一定出來抗議的 DPP會挺資方到底", "push_ipdatetime": "220.129.113.29 01/27 17:12", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "wk105"}, {"push_content": "非因職業因素被隔離 就不能歸責於雇主", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:12", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_content": "跟你老闆說", "push_ipdatetime": "223.136.138.217 01/27 17:13", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "Hooz"}, {"push_content": "自己有病就辭職啊", "push_ipdatetime": "61.227.128.5 01/27 17:13", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "matlab1106"}, {"push_content": "自主隔離=曠工 期滿三天革職論", "push_ipdatetime": "220.129.113.29 01/27 17:14", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "wk105"}, {"push_content": "勞動法規從來沒說被隔離也要去上班", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:14", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_content": "只有說有上班雇主就要付錢給你", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:14", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_content": "你上半天班被通報被抓回去 就付你半天", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:15", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_content": "話說怎麼不從傳染病防制法來看…", "push_ipdatetime": "223.139.82.148 01/27 17:15", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "u9005205"}, {"push_content": "問勞動部只能給四平八穩雙方都不得罪的", "push_ipdatetime": "223.139.82.148 01/27 17:17", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "u9005205"}, {"push_content": "幹那這樣誰要隔離...", "push_ipdatetime": "111.240.88.150 01/27 17:17", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "Blackshirt"}, {"push_content": "答案，新興傳染病就是什麼都還不清楚，", "push_ipdatetime": "223.139.82.148 01/27 17:17", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "u9005205"}, {"push_content": "誰能做主？", "push_ipdatetime": "223.139.82.148 01/27 17:17", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "u9005205"}, {"push_content": "上班了如果搞到其他人也被隔離 致雇主", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:20", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_content": "有損失 小心被勞基法#12無資遣費解職", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:20", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_content": "哈哈不ey自己去跟老闆講", "push_ipdatetime": "223.139.132.124 01/27 17:20", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "poopooking"}, {"push_content": "隔離才不會害到整個公司，資方沒那麼傻", "push_ipdatetime": "114.40.141.35 01/27 17:21", "push_tag": "噓", "push_userid": "yamhome"}, {"push_content": "通常雇主難以舉證損失 但這超好舉證的", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:21", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_content": "本來就該請病假啊", "push_ipdatetime": "101.15.192.125 01/27 17:22", "push_tag": "噓", "push_userid": "jamesbababa"}, {"push_content": "硬要一個可能被感染的員工上班省他14", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.60.240 01/27 17:23", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "zxc1020305"}, {"push_content": "真的很棒，資方都有良心民眾都有自製", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:23", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "力，世界大同。", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:23", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "天薪水的成本 V.S. 公司內部疫情大爆", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.60.240 01/27 17:23", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "zxc1020305"}, {"push_content": "發損失慘重 如果你是老闆你選哪個", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.60.240 01/27 17:23", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "zxc1020305"}, {"push_content": "如果勞方怕被開除去上班，全公司不就挫咧但?", "push_ipdatetime": "36.230.109.179 01/27 17:24", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "uini"}, {"push_content": "樓上一堆人不用幫，老闆腦補，今天勞", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:24", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "動部的公文就是說要上班，不然就花錢", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:24", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "請假。", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:24", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "這不就和颱風假一樣是無薪假 不然你得肺炎", "push_ipdatetime": "110.26.106.187 01/27 17:25", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "mainsa"}, {"push_content": "是公司的錯嗎？", "push_ipdatetime": "110.26.106.187 01/27 17:25", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "mainsa"}, {"push_content": "那你就上班，看多少人因為你請假避禍", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.60.240 01/27 17:25", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "zxc1020305"}, {"push_content": "現，在講的，不是確診肺炎的，現在講", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:26", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "的是居家隔離，他沒有生病呢，政府叫", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:26", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "他去格裡，但是勞動部讓他去上班，我", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:26", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "是不知道這公文霞這邊這麼清楚，大家", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:27", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "一直要幫文字之外的東西做補充有意義", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:27", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "嗎。", "push_ipdatetime": "114.137.194.145 01/27 17:27", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "notepad67"}, {"push_content": "還在凹勞動部說要上班 公文說應上班嗎", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:27", "push_tag": "噓", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_cont