8 01/27 17:35", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "u9005205"}, {"push_content": "因居家隔離-若是小孩也給14天，成人可自理", "push_ipdatetime": "36.230.109.179 01/27 17:35", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "uini"}, {"push_content": "擦不完…", "push_ipdatetime": "223.139.82.148 01/27 17:36", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "u9005205"}, {"push_content": "最後就撐著去上班到整公司都關門讚", "push_ipdatetime": "110.28.104.157 01/27 17:36", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "amALu"}, {"push_content": "吃東西叫外送就好，所以成人的部分應該還好", "push_ipdatetime": "36.230.109.179 01/27 17:36", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "uini"}, {"push_content": "應該向勞動部建議，不然會成為防疫漏洞", "push_ipdatetime": "36.230.109.179 01/27 17:36", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "uini"}, {"push_content": "這種政策 大家會偏向怎麼做 結果會意外嗎?", "push_ipdatetime": "36.238.58.82 01/27 17:36", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "tetani"}, {"push_content": "可討論無病隔離是否符合公假而應給薪", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:37", "push_tag": "噓", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_content": "不要相信台灣勞資方，大家都不想少賺錢der", "push_ipdatetime": "36.230.109.179 01/27 17:37", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "uini"}, {"push_content": "我也不希望我同事這樣 但14天沒錢賺很慘", "push_ipdatetime": "36.238.58.82 01/27 17:38", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "tetani"}, {"push_content": "萬一武漢肺炎最後證實毒性和AB流感差不多", "push_ipdatetime": "36.230.109.179 01/27 17:38", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "uini"}, {"push_content": "為了怕這種事情發生 隱瞞就好了", "push_ipdatetime": "36.238.58.82 01/27 17:38", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "tetani"}, {"push_content": "但硬凹勞動部說要上班還說別人都錯...", "push_ipdatetime": "36.224.214.127 01/27 17:38", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "mirage2000"}, {"push_content": "再來做調整。現在才是剛開始", "push_ipdatetime": "36.230.109.179 01/27 17:38", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "uini"}, {"push_content": "話說SARS都要前例可依，可以做的更好更", "push_ipdatetime": "223.139.82.148 01/27 17:38", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "u9005205"}, {"push_content": "完善，這些都是行政院那些政務次長跨部", "push_ipdatetime": "223.139.82.148 01/27 17:38", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid":